Complete Rule Reference
=======================

ReqShield supports 103 validation rules, covering a vast range of validation scenarios from basic type checks to complex database and conditional logic.

This page serves as a complete reference, categorized for easy lookup.

Basic Type (9)
--------------
* ``required``
* ``filled``
* ``string``
* ``integer``
* ``numeric``
* ``boolean``
* ``array``
* ``nullable``
* ``present``

Format (10)
-----------
* ``email``
* ``url``
* ``active_url``
* ``ip`` (e.g., ``ip``, ``ip:v4``, ``ip:v6,public``)
* ``json``
* ``uuid`` (e.g., ``uuid``, ``uuid:4``)
* ``ulid``
* ``mac``
* ``hex_color``
* ``timezone``

String (12)
-----------
* ``alpha``
* ``alpha_num``
* ``alpha_dash``
* ``ascii``
* ``lowercase``
* ``uppercase``
* ``starts_with:foo,bar``
* ``ends_with:foo,bar``
* ``contains:foo``
* ``doesnt_contain:foo,bar``
* ``doesnt_start_with:foo,bar``
* ``doesnt_end_with:foo,bar``

Numeric (14)
------------
* ``min:value``
* ``max:value``
* ``between:min,max``
* ``size:value``
* ``digits:value``
* ``digits_between:min,max``
* ``min_digits:value``
* ``max_digits:value``
* ``decimal:places``
* ``multiple_of:value``
* ``gt:field`` (Greater Than)
* ``gte:field`` (Greater Than or Equal)
* ``lt:field`` (Less Than)
* ``lte:field`` (Less Than or Equal)

Date/Time (7)
-------------
* ``date``
* ``date_format:format``
* ``date_equals:date``
* ``before:date``
* ``before_or_equal:date``
* ``after:date``
* ``after_or_equal:date``

Conditional (27)
----------------
* ``required_if:field,value``
* ``required_unless:field,value``
* ``required_with:field1,field2``
* ``required_with_all:field1,field2``
* ``required_without:field1,field2``
* ``required_without_all:field1,field2``
* ``required_array_keys:key1,key2``
* ``required_if_accepted:field``
* ``required_if_declined:field``
* ``present_if:field,value``
* ``present_unless:field,value``
* ``present_with:field1,field2``
* ``present_with_all:field1,field2``
* ``missing``
* ``missing_if:field,value``
* ``missing_unless:field,value``
* ``prohibited``
* ``prohibited_if:field,value``
* ``prohibited_unless:field,value``
* ``prohibits:field1,field2``
* ``exclude``
* ``exclude_if:field,value``
* ``exclude_unless:field,value``
* ``exclude_with:field``
* ``exclude_without:field``

Database (2)
------------
* ``unique:table,column``
* ``exists:table,column``

File (6)
--------
* ``file`` (Checks for valid ``is_uploaded_file()``)
* ``image``
* ``mimes:pdf,doc``
* ``mimetypes:application/pdf``
* ``extensions:xls,xlsx``
* ``dimensions`` (For images)

Array (5)
---------
* ``in:foo,bar``
* ``not_in:foo,bar``
* ``in_array:field``
* ``distinct``
* ``is_list`` (Checks for sequential, zero-indexed array)

Comparison (3)
--------------
* ``same:field``
* ``different:field``
* ``confirmed`` (Checks for ``field_confirmation``)

Pattern (2)
-----------
* ``regex:pattern``
* ``not_regex:pattern``

Additional (6)
--------------
* ``accepted`` (e.g., 'yes', 'on', '1', true)
* ``accepted_if:field,value``
* ``declined`` (e.g., 'no', 'off', '0', false)
* ``declined_if:field,value``
* ``bail`` (Stops validation on this field on first failure)
* ``callback`` (Used for custom rules, see :doc:`custom-rules`)
